Zimplats Fourth-Quarter Operating Profit and Platinum Production Rises

-- B y   G o d f r e y   M a r a w a n y i k a
-- 
2011-07-28T16:36:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/zimplats-fourth-quarter-operating-profit-and-platinum-production-rises.html
Zimplats Holdings Ltd. (ZIM) , a unit of
South Africa’s  Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd. (IMP) , posted fourth-
quarter operating profit of $69.6 million compared with $65.6
million in the third quarter, the company said in a statement
released in Zimbabwe today.  Revenue rose 12 percent to $147 million while production
was 103,757 ounces, compared with 85,069 ounces in the third
quarter.  The company hasn’t had a response from government on a
proposal it made to meet the country’s ownership law, Alex
Mhmebere, the company’s chief executive officer, said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Godfrey Marawanyika in Harare at 
 gmarawanyika@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
